title: piano hypnosis
description:
here is some piano hypnosis sessions to help along with my other posted piano lessons , one from Steve g jones and one from instant hypnosis.com

what do they do to help ? 
they are quite effective at reaffirming your commitment to learning the piano and give you a subliminal boost when you need it so to speak.

what they wont do !!
when i purchased these mp3's i imagined them to be able to turn me into Amafukindaeus over night ..lol..(what a sucker) and errrrr well that didnt happen , i did however feel very positive about learning and excited to get back to the piano the following day . When you hit a wall and dont feel like you are making progress these will help you NOT to quit

enjoy the toy
